    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Mode of dress for a fashionable women in the 19th and 20th centuries; dinner dress is less formal than evening wear, ensembles often include sleeves, or open decolletage.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
